onMapLoaded().Description: Called when the map has finished rendering. This will only be called once. You must request another callback if you want to be notified again.

ClassDesc: Callback interface for when the map has finished rendering. This occurs after all tiles required to render the map have been fetched, and all labeling is complete. This event will not fire if the map never loads due to connectivity issues, or if the map is continuously changing and never completes loading due to the user constantly interacting with the map.
